import React from "react"; import { useState } from "react"; import { initializeApp } from 'firebase/app' import { getAuth } from 'firebase/auth' export default function Login() { const [email, setemail] = useState(null); const [password, setpassword] = useState(null); return <>
{setemail(e.target.value)}} value={email}/>
{setpassword(e.target.value)}} value={password}/>
}
